United States: repetition is the mother of wisdom
It is almost comical, with what Schülerstrebsamkeit Barack Obama, the President with his reputation of the brightest, the strategy of his predecessor in the issue of Afghanistan, which for the most stupid.
When he finally his eagerly - awaited ausschwitzte Afghanistan doctrine, it is that he showed on the Kopierpapier from the Bush - Iraq three years ago.
Not only that, in the text itself, he repeatedly used the phrase " as in Iraq, he has even the name of the Bush statement in January 2007 as the name of his own declaration: " new Vorwärtsweg " without hesitation.
He has even three years ago, the Bush idea - fresh troop contributions in the troubled by the civil war in Iraq - as " irresponsible and in their conclusions karastrophische decision ".
Subsequent months showed that the recommendations of the military strategy, the only possible and was very successful, that people today in the news about Iraq.
Bush's reputation has not improved, because he has left his successor a much dankbarere starting situation, as it was to be expected.
In Afghanistan, Barack Obama hopes that the miracle repeatedly.
In order to increase the contingent have again asked the military, especially the supreme commander of the Afghanistan operation, General Stanley McCristal, even despite the Subordinationsgewohnheiten the in the White House.
He called for 40,000 soldiers in order to be able to reverse the situation for the better.
The President has three months, but no better idea and he has the General wenistens about 10,000 soldiers.
From Europe, he has the promise of another 5,000, even though he himself.
Highly problematic about the whole Obama strategy is its plan to withdraw troops from Afghanistan in 18 months, and complete the process within three years. The whole Obama doctrine left more questions than answers.
Some doubt that the increase in the same effect as the measure in Iraq.
Also, despite the fratricidal war in recent years, the Iraq is relatively well - structured, honor the values.
The Afghan situation is characterised by the kontraindikation - it can rely on no one and there are no agreements.
Under these circumstances, it is difficult to prepare the Afghan security forces, which are used every day to change their mind.
The political institutions, even if they were established formally correct, that leaves only buildings, behind which the patriarchal tribe relations further.
The balance of interests between the various ethnic groups is unusually complicated, particularly because of the confusion of the conditions that the Pakistan and Iran influences.
The building of a " strong state ", which is the minimalist objective of the whole operation is very unrealistic.
Time horizon of the Obama strategy surprised by his voluntarism
Over the last eight years, the situation in Afghanistan and now it is on the verge of explosion.
To believe that the small soldiers in the war cries broke out on the " Homecoming " is a miracle, can only create a truly romantic soul, is not influenced by facts.
From the political point of view is the date for the withdrawal of irresponsibility, because the Taliban as the indirect confession of American defeat.
The last NATO summit showed that the willingness of the Europeans to participate in the fighting in Afghanistan, is running out.
Europe's politicians cannot and do not want to explain to their constituents, in what way the security of Germany or Italy with the war in the Hindu Kush Gebirgsvorland.
Another possible factor that can influence the situation radically, is the development of events in Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and the increased sanctions on the Iranians do not work, the United States is a very serious question of whether or not to solve the problem with troops.
This question must be answered in the period in which America after Obama the winner withdrawal from Afghanistan.
Any solution will also mean a dramatic turn of the Afghan situation.
The only consolation plaster for Barack Obama is the fact that three years left before the presidential election, and therefore, there is still enough time, so that he can resort to a different strategy, would prove to be a total loss.
