In addition, all the staff of the Samstags class fares and lunch.
With that in mind, that the overtime of the most urgent and most burning issue in demands and complaints of trade unionists were last week, the production has the management yesterday afternoon with immediate effect on the lifting of all overtime for the month of December, decided on.
The staff of the automobile factory until last week had been forced to work virtually every day after the Achtstundenschicht 2 overtime.
