His association already in the long term for the Pneumokokken vaccination.
The experts at the international conference, which was involved in our union, were not very satisfied that we have voluntary vaccination.
This is not ideal.
On the other hand, we are pleased that we have succeeded, at least.
I believe that this is the way we must go now, Kalovsky led.
The Department of Health wants but the vaccination procedure against Pneumokokken change.
At this moment, we are not at all, said his spokesman Vlastimil Sesen.
The voluntary vaccination has its drawbacks, doctors say.
