Manager revolution or the end of the Strategic early education?
If nothing changes in the leadership of the major French companies, our fight for the development of economic intelligence in vain ...
For more than a decade, the attitude of the management of large companies in relation to his staff, said the position of consumers from the marketing revolution: it is For the staff to join " values " determines the best, as it was earlier in the consumer - products of the technicians in the station.
By customers in the heart of the company has the marketing revolution the strategies of the conquest of the markets in the ground ... although the authoritarian temptation products separately factors preferences of customers to impose regularly again!
A demobilisation of staff can lead to a deadly demoralisation.
The suicides at France Telecom, PSA and Renault are only the tip of a much larger phenomenon, in particular the employees affected.
These demobilisation has a negative impact on the development of all intellectual functions of the company, in particular those of R& Eund, what is even more crucial to those of economic intelligence.
In fact, the IU (Intelligence Economique = economic intelligence) " of all the parties involved (...) a proactive approach and a forward - looking vision "; it by the staff, which the instructions of the authoritarian management.
That is why we are calling for an occupational revolution, which would be the staff of the concerns of the company on an equal footing with the customers.
The very - related benefits of internal polls
The internal polls, as the questionnaire, the Orange has made his, this revolution in relation to the management practice?
I fear that, unfortunately, not.
- First, because I could see that the whole structure with a new situation after many detours, finally, to do ... what it has always done.
Also because the authoritarianism - one of the pathologies of power in proportion to the importance of his own failures.
And finally, because most of the leaders have a very simple idea of human behavior.
Emerged from the great engineering schools is their interpretation of psychology mechanistic.
They play by intellectual comfort the old behavioristische theory, which was recently by the American " neuroscience " and unknowingly far - reaching research institutes and through the media.
Thus, and it suggests that it is possible, the " leverage " (sic) on the involvement of employees, a aktuellein Le Figaro. fr survey by Ipsos executives in a position to a mechanistic control system, which is unsuitable for today's world.
The mobilisation factors identify and measure
Instead, for the smooth operation of the modern business the adoption of a final view of human behavior.
It is, in any idea or practice of steering a fundamental minutes: for the wage - earners is the commitment to the company will only be possible if it clearly as a means to achieve a portion of their dreams, their ambition and their projects.
Currently only the studies from the multifunctional analysis of this idea of the motivation of staff.
These studies have shown that their companies on the basis of a Doxa judge them by their perceived image of the company, to assess what it offers them to achieve their life goals.
Thanks to the identification and the measurement of these factors can predict the executives of the companies ' social performance and anticipate and human resource management back to the right place.
So they create a fertile ground for the harmonious development of a robust and effective economic intelligence.
