New programmes for the evaluation of vehicles
In these days of storms and accidents not only deserve the motor workshops
Every day, thousands of vehicles were involved in an accident, in the workshops, where a experts assess the damage and the cost of the repair.
Not a single accident is the same and the calculation of the cost of the parts and working hours can be a long and complicated task.
The calculation of the repair cost of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros by hand, including the parts and working hours, can take up to two or three hours.
It is, however, with the support of the latest computer tools a matter of minutes
That is why almost 100% of the experts use this type of systems.
The services and application providers for the assessment of accidents and repair the information they receive from the manufacturers to deal with their customers in the form of a useful programme.
In Spain, part of the American group Solera, the market leader; 80% of all opinions, with their products.
The other two companies, with the Tool - market for evaluation and draw up a report, GtMotive and Eurotax.
The work with the data, which the manufacturers, is anything but simple.
According to Eduardo Velázquez, sales manager of Audatex, with 63 manufacturers and importers, with each and every one of them the information in a different format.
In addition to the growing amount of data, to the point that in the last five years more versions, variants and Motorisierungen came on the market than in the 15 years before.
As soon as a new car on the market, starting for the company's work.
It is a difficult task, because jedeseinzelnde of thousands of vehicles must be katagolisiert and its price.
In addition, each model of an " intelligent " Graphikbild, on the different parts of the vehicle, " click. "
If it is a great sold model, the work can be completed in a week, if the process is progressing quickly.
If it is a less gebräuchliches car, it can take up to three or four months. at present, Audatex in 2% in Spain displaced on full information.
Among the more rarefied models they have, for example, information about the Porsche models, but not on Ferrari or Lamborghini.
In relation to the car park at the Straβen over 99%.
For the implementation of the documentation and the production of databases, Audatex worldwide on eight (Spain, France, Germany, the United States, Brazil, Mexico, China and Japan) distributed centres and each of them has in certain brands.
The national headquarters is located in Alcobendas (Madrid) .
There are more than a hundred technicians (usually experts for mechanics) simultaneously with three computer screens.
Audatex invested 90 million euros a year in the preparation of these databases.
Every month, they take 2.5 million data on their customers get the updates every second day.
The drafting of this enormous flow of information allows companies to use these in various ways and to offer different products.
The most common use is the use of the repairs and repair, but there are, depending on the country also tools for the management of scrap metal parts or for the calculation of the or residual value of a car.
The only businesses that have a leader who informed about the value of used cars in Spain, is Eurotax.
Audatex provides this offer in Spain, but in the United States.
In the view of the products that can be easily an overview of the kind of support they industry experts.
This company offers ten different tools, is the star of the products AudaPlus, a standard solution to Begutachutng of accidents for the experts.
It involves vehicles, motorcycles and light and heavy industrial vehicles.
In addition to the cost of the parts, it contains the estimated by the manufacturer or the Lackierungspreise.
This tool is depending on the intended use, that is, for every opinion, paid.
The most expensive it will be for customers, it rarely, a maximum of ten times in the month, 5.75 per month.
By contrast, every insurance company, which carries out the thousands of opinions, the price with Audatex.
In other products, such as AudaVIN, can be a vehicle and equipment with which it ran from the installation band, only by the chassis number.
AudaGlass deals with the car windows, and AudaSubastas is a for the specialist market open service on the Internet, with the one for vehicles that have been declared a total loss, can offer.
The statistics service is very useful in identifying trends, the implementation of geodemographischen analyses or for the purpose of obtaining information about the derogations for brand and model.
You can, for example, how many models of a particular car because of breakdowns in the garage or how many of them in a certain period of time were involved in a serious accident.
Gt motives is the only Spanish company, which is the development of this type of computer tools.
Distributing It among other Gt Estimate, which also is intended for consultants and on the same kind of digital images, access to parts or prices and official working hours of the manufacturer.
Gt motives is a company of the group Einsa, which was founded in 1971 as a provider of services and solutions to the assessment of damage, breakdowns or Wartungen of vehicles.
The GT - leader for advice is a reference product on the market.
They work with 24,000 users in garages, 3, 100 accountants and 53 insurance companies.
Their volume of business has increased in the last three years, with 20% per year and 2008 the turnover of EUR 10.8 million.
At the beginning of last year, they began to go on the international market with the opening of an office in Paris.
Audatex was founded in Germany in 1966 and 1979 in Spain.
According to sources of the company 62% of its business in Europe and the rest of the world, and the remaining 38% in North and South America. They work with 900 insurance companies and 33,000 workshops, 3,000 of them in Spain.
The total turnover in the world of the group Solera (Audatex, Sidexa, Informex, ABZ, Hollander and IMS) amounts to $557 million, more than in 2008.
The company has revenues of EUR 19.1 million, more than in the previous year.
In 2005, the group Solera $1 billion in the stock market and today their shares at a value of $2.4 billion.
Since the year 2007, they are on the New York Stock Exchange and part of the reference index Standard& Poor's.
Auction of accident cars on the Internet
Last October, the group bought a car online Plattfom on the Internet for the sale of Unfallfahrzeugen and motorcycles.
The purchase meant the payment of 59,5 million for 85% of the capital of the society, which could increase next year to the remaining 15%.
The purpose of this Kaufes was to offer its customers more services and value, with the possibility of access to a riesigeen international market.
This Begutachtungs and purchasing service is exclusively to industry professionals, such as insurance companies, consultants, car rental companies, workshops, and car dealers, who register their activities.
This platform was founded in 1996 in Germany and manages more than 650,000 operations across Europe, 500,000 of them in Germany alone.
Its main markets are Spain, Greece, Poland and Turkey.
The website has more than 1,500 registered sellers and 4,000 consultants.
Every day, 3,000 ads and on the Spanish market every day, 100 new ads.
According to the Spanish legislation, a vehicle whose Fahrgestellnumer abgemeldet, was no longer on the streets, it must be used, however, certain not damaged parts as spare parts.
The cars with historical value, must be approved again, even if they were abgemeldet after difficult authorities corridors.
Cost estimates of the workshop in four stages
With the tool Auda - Taller, the company Audatex ensures that the user in only four stages a cost estimate: identification of the vehicle, search of spare parts, and a cost estimate.
The ease of use of these systems is a fundamental condition, especially in order to convince the older professionals, who are usually more or less against the use of these new computer techniques.
The database includes 1.034 vehicles, 666 of them are passenger cars, 109 SUVs, 137 motorcycles, 78 vans and trucks.
Of course, you need to use a computer with Internet connection.
After the repair model based on the chassis number have been identified, a graphic overview of the model and will then select the needed spare parts.
The user can include variables, such as the price for the working hours, Aufpreise or rebates and then he can leave the cost estimates and pass on to its customers.
AudaTaller, however, is not a tool for evaluating how AudaPlus, but rather a reference list.
The main difference between the two systems is that it contains no aimed at dieWerkstatt estimated working hours.
The use of this tool 350 euros per year, an amount that the customer can easily pay.
At present, the company to be able to offer these images in three - dimensional format.
It is an innovation in the auto mechanics can wait for a long time, choose, for example, a door and complete the picture can look at the inner side.
